\n同埋你所講既溫和咁解釋革命"},{"pid":"49991bc5b76712f8221fdec731123c837484027f","tid":1423923,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7214050e111a7dcfe2715587e2db5c75f39d3c","tid":1423923,"uid":44751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/di91BGs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdi91BGs.png&h=5633db2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"一切以天琦原有嘅意思為基本答案"},{"pid":"3b054cdf4b7238d45d06ceea06eab5aab80e701c","tid":1423923,"uid":104489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"應該文宣/民間記者會上面  同公眾解釋口號意思<br />\n主動拎返個話語權，唔可以任由對方定性"},{"pid":"c3db4068f5d9c60e56d2a99f83862e03ec77ffc0","tid":1423923,"uid":279266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49991bc5b76712f8221fdec731123c837484027f","tid":1423923,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7214050e111a7dcfe2715587e2db5c75f39d3c","tid":1423923,"uid":44751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/di91BGs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdi91BGs.png&h=5633db2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"一切以天琦原有嘅意思為基本答案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"嗯<br />\n要具體化<br />\n太抽象港豬跟唔上"},{"pid":"5e54de0f5aa22619909498b6e7bc1fc3f17520a6","tid":1423923,"uid":296375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ff7ec78baf597dfb0561bcbdbaf49d607dc896","tid":1423923,"uid":296375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1) 光復香港 - 我地要由<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>林奠 警黑勢力 保皇黨</strong></span>既手中<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拯救香港同埋為香港被捕既義士!!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2) 時代革命 - 我地係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>改變